steps.name: I open the Ghost login page
I navigate to the tags page
I navigate to the tags page
I enter to create a new tag
I enter tag details "Original Tag Name" "Sample tag description"
I navigate to the tags page
I select the tag to edit "Original Tag Name"
I should not see the tag "Post to Delete" in the tags list
